f0c","tid":1346293,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d3ce24a39259ea0fdfe5cb52e494bd08df1c62","tid":1346293,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">適用於住喺元朗嘅澳洲公民</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nenquiries.hongkong@dfat.gov.au<br />\n<br />\nDear Sir/Madam<br />\n<br />\nI am an Australian citizen residing in Yuen Long District writing to express my concern and request appropriate actions regarding the violence by alleged triads. I was unable to seek assistance from the local police.<br />\n<br />\nIt is trusted that the local news coverage has been sufficient to illustrate the worsening situation.<br />\n<br />\nI am awaiting for your response as I am relying on public transportation for daily commute.<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention and hope to hear from you soon.<br />\n<br />\nBest regards<br />\n[你個名]"},{"pid":"f1cf9bceb97c07891840948756ab7490e9385c6b","tid":1346293,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跟返自己生日月份，睇返搵邊個講元朗既事</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>【一月、二月】 David R. Stilwell</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fbiographies%2Fdavid-r-stilwell%2F&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=857cb3f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【三月】 Mitch McConnell</strong><br />\nEmail：senator@mcconnell.senate.gov<br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mcconnellpress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmcconnellpress&d=kdu